tags.name: elmsln-loading
tags.description:
`elmsln-loading`
A spinner to tell the user that something is loading.
This is just the spinner though and doesn't provide any text or anything else.

Attributes:

  * `color` {`string`} - color

  * `size` {`string`} - tiny, small, medium, large, epic sizing.

Properties:

  * `color` {`string`} - color

  * `size` {`string`} - tiny, small, medium, large, epic sizing.

attributes.name: size
attributes.description:
`size` {`string`} - tiny, small, medium, large, epic sizing.

Property: size

Default: medium
